Class EXTEfx

java.lang.Object
org.lwjgl.openal.EXTEfx
public class EXTEfx extends Object
Native bindings to the ALC_EXT_EFX extension.

The Effects Extension is designed to provide a generic, cross-platform framework for adding advanced DSP effects to OpenAL.
